7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=e2d621bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=d3db0eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=b9c56dd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"5ecb7676bd5baa028a25cc541400b2eec02c10a9","tid":1670551,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"希望佢平安無事"},{"pid":"0949fa575d19fa50964efc4f28b1854ec3b1e9eb","tid":1670551,"uid":292091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"佢真係玩命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05388a5b42ef3df2ee8789c7a077d8fd0004b44a","tid":1670551,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:54:26.000Z","msg":"佢真勇"},{"pid":"2d8bc63fdfde07137069f7f284482ca8d4f7c59c","tid":1670551,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58794bcdec0557d5a9b151256f764ba043fec55e","tid":1670551,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"乜都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a548f421852b95580f7880a2af9a5f13205cb77","tid":1670551,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"好快有得政治避難"},{"pid":"a572283ac21379d778cedde7b1272661821ed4c3","tid":1670551,"uid":333203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:04:03.000Z","msg":"佢微信名叫 陳秋實【不移民】<br />\n<br />\n好多人提出免費幇佢移民<br />\n<br />\n佢一概拒絕"},{"pid":"70a6d2be21c175511c5ebbf6a007c1cfaa70ebc1","tid":1670551,"uid":333203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2djzXQu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2djzXQu.jpg&h=24fe066a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}